1. Replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE with actual JWT from login response
2. Replace VENUE_ID_FROM_DB with actual venue ID from database
3. TIME SLOTS: 9-11, 11-1, 2-4, 4-6
4. Email notifications require setup in .env
5. Use same date with different time slots to test approval flow
